metadata.name: You're Lying But Ok  #1
metadata.description:
A lyric nft exploring the common human to attempt to heal all of our ills via romantic love. 

ONLY collectors will receive the full song via a token-gated link on Tellie. 

Lyrics + Vox + Vocal Mixing by Shxdw 
Produced by Grl 
Audio Mix + Master by Richard Richaid 
Visuals by Jesse Soleil
Typography Animation  by Ren
